          "username": "jhh"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-09-05 15:54:43.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nNo problem.  May be we can create a jira task to move away from FlexLogger and just use a portable SLF4J logger that uses logback.xml underneath.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
